OL,6,FThese comments reflect the need for a
OL,7,Ffunding model which achieves certain
OL,8,Fkey purposes which supporters of the
OL,9,FBBC would be unlikely to ever question.
OL,11,
OL,12,F Everyone should have the same range
OL,13,Fof programmes and services to choose
OL,14,Fbetween ` regardless of ability to pay.
OL,15,F The BBC should be free from
OL,16,Fcommercial interests.
OL,17,F The BBC should not be open to
OL,18,Fgovernment influence.
