OL,6,FBut are there better alternatives to
OL,7,Fthe licence fee which still respect
OL,8,Fthe BBC's purpose and independence?
OL,10,FMr Shah discusses the prospect of a
OL,11,Fhousehold levy ` paid by every
OL,12,Fhousehold regardless of whether they
OL,13,Fown a TV set.
OL,15,FHe also discusses enforcement issues
OL,16,Fand the need for such a charge to be
OL,17,Fprogressive.
OL,19,FObvious possibilities include linking
OL,20,Fany household levy to income tax bands
OL,21,For council tax bands to create a
OL,22,Fsliding scale.
