OL,6,FIt is a fascinating debate which all
OL,7,Fof us who support the BBC and public
OL,8,Fservice broadcasting should not shy
OL,9,Faway from.
OL,11,FITV's latest financial results last
OL,12,Fweek again demonstrated the
OL,13,Fchallenging marketplace.
OL,15,FBut I am also reminded of another key
OL,16,Fargument.
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G6/11
