OL,6,FAs long as the BBC in one form or
OL,7,Fanother reaches the vast majority of
OL,8,Fhouseholds in the country with
OL,9,Fservices which are distinct from those
OL,10,Fthe market might provide, it is hard
OL,11,Ffor those who seek to undermine the
OL,12,Fcorporation to make hay.
OL,14,FThis fundamentally means high quality
OL,15,Fprogrammes ` some of which are
OL,16,Fpopular, all of which have public
OL,17,Fservice values.
OL,19,FIt also means flagship services like
OL,20,FBBC One need to be on top form.
