OL,6,FLast week's episodes of Panorama from
OL,7,FUkraine and Imagine were the kind of
OL,8,Fprogrammes no mainstream commercial
OL,9,Fchannel would commission or broadcast
OL,10,Fexcept to fulfil a straightforward
OL,11,Fregulatory requirement.
OL,13,FThere are other examples in the
OL,14,Fschedule ` including popular
OL,15,Fprogrammes a commercial channel might
OL,16,Fnever have supported in the first
OL,17,Fplace like Antiques Roadshow and
OL,18,FCountryfile.
OL,20,FBut can more be done to highlight the
OL,21,FBBC's distinctive character without
OL,22,Frisking a loss of ratings?
