OL,6,FAnd while it is perfectly acceptable
OL,7,Ffor serious programmes to achieve
OL,8,Fmodest ratings, would the likes of
OL,9,FWaterloo Road be better off on BBC
OL,10,FThree? It works well for some
OL,11,Fdemographics but lacks widespread
OL,12,Fappeal for a core BBC One audience and
OL,13,Fgets awful overnight ratings.
OL,15,FLast week brought brilliant news for
OL,16,Ffootball fans: Scotland, Wales and
OL,17,FNorthern Ireland internationals will
OL,18,Fbe on BBC TV and the iPlayer.
OL,20,FIn Scotland in particular, the fact
OL,21,Fthese games had been on pay channels
OL,22,Fwas controversial.
