OL,6,FEngland internationals will remain on
OL,7,FITV.
OL,9,FWhile ITV's match coverage is
OL,10,Fexcellent, the need for large amounts
OL,11,Fof advertising at half time mean
OL,12,Fdiscussion and analysis is restricted.
OL,14,FCan the BBC make a positive virtue of
OL,15,Fwhat it can do?
OL,17,FYou only need to contrast the
OL,18,Fpresentation of Six Nations games on
OL,19,FBBC One with those on ITV 1.
