OL,6,FThe extra editorial time surrounding
OL,7,Fthe matches and at half time can make
OL,8,Fa big difference.
OL,10,FBeing distinctive is not always about
OL,11,Fself-conscious innovation or serving
OL,12,Fminorities.
OL,14,FIt is about showing that the BBC can
OL,15,Fbring added value to all kinds of
OL,16,Fprogrammes and services.
OL,18,FThat point needs to be driven home to
OL,19,Fhelp ensure that paying for the BBC `
OL,20,Fwhether through the licence fee or a
OL,21,Freformed system ` doesn't feel like
OL,22,Fpaying a tax.
